  "detailed_description": "This game is a puzzle game in which you switch between two perspectives, one viewed from the side and the other viewed from above, aiming for the goal window.<br>The biggest feature is that when you change the viewpoint, the depth and height also change.<br>Please enjoy the mysterious feeling that \"the brain is buggy\".<br><br>It is a puzzle game that switches between the viewpoint from the side and the viewpoint from above.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618220/extras/8c92f51377f0cebaeb0910e5321bb5a5.poster.avif?t=1628840087\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618220/extras/8c92f51377f0cebaeb0910e5321bb5a5.webm?t=1628840087\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618220/extras/8c92f51377f0cebaeb0910e5321bb5a5.mp4?t=1628840087\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Seen from the side, the stacked wooden boxes feel heavy and cannot be moved, but ...<br>Seen from above, it feels only the weight of one wooden box, so it can be moved.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618220/extras/3c007c61403083cedb803c5d2352a365.poster.avif?t=1628840087\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618220/extras/3c007c61403083cedb803c5d2352a365.webm?t=1628840087\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618220/extras/3c007c61403083cedb803c5d2352a365.mp4?t=1628840087\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Seen from above, the blocks and stairs are separated, but ...<br>It doesn't look like it's far away from the side, so you can ride on the block.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618220/extras/1879941608559fe80e770ce3b129b703.poster.avif?t=1628840087\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618220/extras/1879941608559fe80e770ce3b129b703.webm?t=1628840087\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618220/extras/1879941608559fe80e770ce3b129b703.mp4?t=1628840087\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Seen from the side, you can't get on the stacked wooden boxes, but ...<br>When viewed from above, there is no difference in height between the block and the wooden box, so you can ride on the wooden box.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618220/extras/83074ee19e6d0a02605295e3460ea553.poster.avif?t=1628840087\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618220/extras/83074ee19e6d0a02605295e3460ea553.webm?t=1628840087\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618220/extras/83074ee19e6d0a02605295e3460ea553.mp4?t=1628840087\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "This game is a puzzle game in which you switch between two perspectives, one viewed from the side and the other viewed from above, aiming for the goal window.<br>The biggest feature is that when you change the viewpoint, the depth and height also change.<br>Please enjoy the mysterious feeling that \"the brain is buggy\".<br><br>It is a puzzle game that switches between the viewpoint from the side and the viewpoint from above.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618220/extras/8c92f51377f0cebaeb0910e5321bb5a5.poster.avif?t=1628840087\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618220/extras/8c92f51377f0cebaeb0910e5321bb5a5.webm?t=1628840087\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618220/extras/8c92f51377f0cebaeb0910e5321bb5a5.mp4?t=1628840087\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Seen from the side, the stacked wooden boxes feel heavy and cannot be moved, but ...<br>Seen from above, it feels only the weight of one wooden box, so it can be moved.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618220/extras/3c007c61403083cedb803c5d2352a365.poster.avif?t=1628840087\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618220/extras/3c007c61403083cedb803c5d2352a365.webm?t=1628840087\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618220/extras/3c007c61403083cedb803c5d2352a365.mp4?t=1628840087\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Seen from above, the blocks and stairs are separated, but ...<br>It doesn't look like it's far away from the side, so you can ride on the block.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618220/extras/1879941608559fe80e770ce3b129b703.poster.avif?t=1628840087\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618220/extras/1879941608559fe80e770ce3b129b703.webm?t=1628840087\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618220/extras/1879941608559fe80e770ce3b129b703.mp4?t=1628840087\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Seen from the side, you can't get on the stacked wooden boxes, but ...<br>When viewed from above, there is no difference in height between the block and the wooden box, so you can ride on the wooden box.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618220/extras/83074ee19e6d0a02605295e3460ea553.poster.avif?t=1628840087\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618220/extras/83074ee19e6d0a02605295e3460ea553.webm?t=1628840087\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618220/extras/83074ee19e6d0a02605295e3460ea553.mp4?t=1628840087\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
